    "body": "I found a bug.\r\nhttps://deploy-preview-2408--algolia-instantsearch.netlify.com/dev-novel/?selectedStory=RangeSlider.default \r\n\r\n- set the price slider to > 2000 (2000 is the min)\r\n- type 'mg'\r\n- end up a slider with range outside the min max returned by the results\r\n- remove the query\r\n- range is now 600 - 2000",
